Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer, Lot 716 at Ravenhall Way, a 1,861sqm* titled block of land ready for development, with an existing permit approved for 3 warehouses, for sale. 

This block is located on Ravenhall Way, Ravenhall in the Orbis Estate on Robinsons Road. This Commercial 2 zoned estate will benefit from the Robinsons Road upgrade in the coming years. 

This upgrade will improve road access, benefitting logistics occupiers. It will also ensure the amenity in the area is increased to cater for this prosperous industrial and commercial area of Melbourne’s west.  

The property is located minutes from Robinsons Road interchange offering direct access to the Western Freeway and Western Ring Road. 

Please contact the exclusively appointed agents for pricing, title and working drawings. 

+ Dimensions 31m* x 60m*.

For more information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team. 

*approximate

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fully serviced industrial lots for sale

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is thrilled to exclusively offer to market – Infinity Industrial Estate, Ravenhall. An industrial 3 zoned estate, Infinity is the only small lot industrial land release in Melbourne’s booming west. 

Connected to one of Australia’s most important freight corridors on the edge of Australia’s fastest-growing city, positioning your business in Infinity Industrial Estate is an opportunity that will sell out quickly. 

A tightly held market in an established residential and commercial catchment, Infinity Industrial Estate offers a range of options perfectly suited for businesses both large and small.

Key logistics locations are easily accessed via two routes to Melbourne’s freeway network:

+  1km* to Western Freeway on/off ramp – Christies Road, Ravenhall
+  2.5km* to Western Freeway on/off ramp – Robinsons Road, Derrimut/Truganina
+  13km* to Melbourne Airport
+  14km* to Port of Melbourne
+  18km* to Melbourne CBD (Spencer St)
+  13km* Melton
+  22km* to Hume Freeway
+  52km* to Avalon Airport
+  48km* to Geelong
+  80km* to Ballarat

For further information, please contact the CBRE team. 

*approx.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Building Permit for Place of Worship

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer to the market 81 Eucumbene Drive, Ravenhall, for sale.

The site is located within Ravenhall’s most sought after business park and offers immediate access to the Western Freeway. Westlink Estate is home to occupants such as Bunnings Warehouse, Officeworks, Fantastic Furniture, Autobarn, Derrimut Gym, Avis Car and Truck Rental, Chipmunks Playcentre and a host of car dealerships.

The closest freeway on ramp is less than a kilometre away and provides immediate access to bustling Ballarat Road.

81 Eucumbene Drive is well positioned to take advantage of a host of strong industrial sales results within the immediate area and will look to be prosperous for the successful purchaser.

Further, this site comes with a highly desirable permit for a place of worship with approved plans and is ripe for immediate development.

Key attributes:
+ Total site area: 5,613sqm*
+ Dimensions: 100 metres* long x 56.3 metres* wide
+ Building permit for place of worship
+ Industrial 3 Zone
+ Suitable for a range of industrial development opportunities (STCA).

To view a copy of the Information Memorandum featuring permit and plans, or for any further details, please contact the CBRE.

*approximate
